profile:
Copper Expressions is a professional, reliable, fully insured and responsible company which will work with you to design and install a professional quality outdoor lighting system that meets your needs.  We design our systems using products that are developed and engineered to last for many years, with only minimal regular maintenance to continuously enhance the beauty of your property.
A professional outdoor lighting system is an investment to your home or business and provides safety, security, beauty and more time to enjoy your property in the evening.  We will work with you to develop a system that is totally automated, reliable, and will enhance your landscape, but provide additional security and safety to your home or business environment. We are very comfortable working with your landscape professional, or designing a system to work with existing landscapes and outdoor spaces on your property.
